title: Secretary-General of Bahraini Cabinet receives UAE Ambassador (Ministry of Foreign Affairs of the United Arab ...
text: (Source: Ministry of Foreign Affairs of the United Arab Emirates) â€‹HE Abdulridha Abdullah Mahmoud Khori, UAE Ambassador to the Kingdom of Bahrain, and HE Dr. Yasser bin Isa Al-Nasser, Bahraini Cabinet Secretary-General, have discussed bilateral relations between the two countries and ways of boosting them in various fields. During the meeting, Al-Nasser commended the strong relations between the Kingdom of Bahrain and the United Arab Emirates.
